And all twenty five shots hit was the ocean floor. Unless Alecto had 
night vision on all she would see is the bursts of light from some of 
the autoguns. THe sun doesnt reach as far down as the second 
infecticon base is. A moment later 10 autoguns fired on Alecto, each 
sending 5 shots for a total of 50 her way. At the same time, 5 
missile turrets each opened fire on her sending 5 concussion missiles 
at her. Inside Blight laughed evily as he ran his finger tips up to 
two areas of the black console infront of him. A moment later, a 
large cannon aimed at Alecto and fired a particle beam at her.
